  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job Description</strong></u></p><p>- Responsible for the Quantity Surveying and Contract Administration.</p><p>- Study and identify discrepancies in tender/contract documents and raise queries for clarifications</p><p>- Source for quotations from subcontractors/suppliers, assist for evaluation and comparison for the received quotations and produce quantity measurement within targeted timeline</p><p><u><strong>Job Requirements</strong></u></p><p>- Highly motivated, self-driven with initiatives to work independently. Able to work in a fast paced and dynamic environment <br /><br />- Good negotiation, interpersonal skills and a team player</p><p>- Attention to detail and methodical approach to work</p><p>- Diploma or above in Quantity Surveying or equivalent</p><p>- At least 3 years of experience as a Quantity Surveyor<br /><br />- Proficient in MS Office</p>",
